CPP 2005 Project, Communication Classes
---------------------------------------
- 'make' makes the library libclientserver.a.
- 'make' makes the executables client, MemoryServer and DiskServer.
- The subdirectory scr contains the files used for the program. The file DiskServer.cc
  is the server using a database on the disk and the file MemoryServer.cc is a server
  using in-memory storage. Aswell as other classes used by the servers.
